取其輕<br />\n<br />\nDon&rsquo;t blame the victim"},{"pid":"c8265b06bb7ca652c685167b79c9b17b190a6890","tid":1736023,"uid":318612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"Sorry借一借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家成日都話手足唔係condom,<br />\n咁我地聽朝一齊去支持佢地</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUHmpHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUHmpHa.jpg&h=8a668bc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f5fd08349d91a62fb43c45d86044a0df3283389","tid":1736023,"uid":336769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【唔好自己出黎，留守扮受害者最好】</span></span><br />\n雖然知PolyU夠勇，但<span style=\"color: red;\">popo明顯係唔想攻入去</span>，因為一攻入去就會輸哂國際線，加上法律上唔夠料告得入，佢只想你自己出黎，<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講&quot;投降&quot;/ &quot;自首&quot;</span></span></span>，千祈唔好中佢地計，已經好多人中左計被捕。<br />\n<br />\n留番係PolyU，有必要可以落Gear [反正唔應該再衝]。你地要扮 Victim，到時真係被人餓死左，國際線好易打。<span style=\"color: red;\">被捕時一定要Press影住</span>。街坊唔好講明去增援/開缺口，反而用<span style=\"color: red;\">人道理由</span>要求開路，運送食物+FA，要國際傳媒影住，popo唔俾，就加強我地國際線。<br />\n<br />\n既然<span style=\"color: red;\">命得一條，就要好好善用</span>，人地重狗，我地唔可以跌入圏套行出去，唔好跟佢地劇本。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港諗緊計，Stay Strong</span><br />\n<br />\n永遠支持PolyU!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">Btw, 留意假記者/FA/政客/社工。</span>"}]}